statements.sql: select `n`.*, `u`.`user_id`, `u`.`username`, `u`.`user_dp`, `u`.`login_type`, GROUP_CONCAT(n.notify_id SEPARATOR ',') as notify_ids, DATE_FORMAT(n.added_on, '%Y-%m-%d') as date, `uv`.`verified`, count(n.type) as notify_total from `notifications` as `n` inner join `users` as `u` on `u`.`user_id` = `n`.`notify_by` left join `user_verify` as `uv` on `uv`.`user_id` = `u`.`user_id` and `uv`.`verified` = 'A' where (`n`.`notify_to` = 0) and `n`.`type` not in ('UF', 'UL') and `n`.`read` = 0 group by `date`, `n`.`type` order by `n`.`added_on` desc

select `v`.`video`, `v`.`user_id` from `videos` as `v` left join `users` as `u` on `u`.`user_id` = `v`.`user_id` where `u`.`active` = 1 and `u`.`deleted` = 0 and `v`.`active` = 1 and `v`.`flag` = 0 and `v`.`privacy` = 0 and `v`.`deleted` = 0 order by RAND() limit 1

select v.user_id, v.video_id,u.username, v.video,v.title,v.description, v.thumb, v.gif, v.total_likes, v.total_comments, v.total_views, ifnull(l.like_id, 0) as liked,uv.verified as verified,u.user_dp,CONCAT(u.fname," ",u.lname) as name,v.total_comments from `videos` as `v` left join `likes` as `l` on `l`.`video_id` = `v`.`video_id` and  l.user_id=0 left join `user_verify` as `uv` on `uv`.`user_id` = `v`.`user_id` and `uv`.`verified` = 'A' inner join `users` as `u` on `u`.`user_id` = `v`.`user_id` where `v`.`privacy` = 0 and (`v`.`active` = 1 and `v`.`enabled` = 1 and `u`.`active` = 1 and `v`.`flag` = 0) order by RAND() limit 9 offset 0

select count(*) as aggregate from `videos` as `v` left join `likes` as `l` on `l`.`video_id` = `v`.`video_id` and  l.user_id=0 left join `user_verify` as `uv` on `uv`.`user_id` = `v`.`user_id` and `uv`.`verified` = 'A' inner join `users` as `u` on `u`.`user_id` = `v`.`user_id` where `v`.`privacy` = 0 and (`v`.`active` = 1 and `v`.`enabled` = 1 and `u`.`active` = 1 and `v`.`flag` = 0 and `v`.`privacy` = 0)

select u.user_id,u.username,u.fname,u.lname,u.user_dp,ifnull(f2.follow_id,0) as follow,uv.verified from `users` as `u` left join `user_verify` as `uv` on `uv`.`user_id` = `u`.`user_id` and `uv`.`verified` = 'A' left join `follow` as `f2` on `u`.`user_id` = `f2`.`follow_to` and `f2`.`follow_by` = 0 where `u`.`user_id` != 0 and `active` = 1 and `deleted` = 0 group by u.user_id,u.username,u.fname,u.lname,u.user_dp order by `user_id` desc limit 5
